MCU 8051 IDE - EBUILD
---------------------


Instalation (Gentoo Linux only):
-------------------------------

A) Automatical installation
	# ./install.sh
	# emerge -va mcu8051ide

B) Manual instalation
	1. Gain superuser rights
		# su
	2. Create directory for local portage overlay and create category
		# mkdir -p /usr/local/portage/dev-embedded/mcu8051ide
	3. Copy there the ebuild
		# cp mcu8051ide-1.3.5.ebuild /usr/local/portage/dev-embedded/mcu8051ide/
	4. Create ebuild manifest (or something)
		# ebuild /usr/local/portage/dev-embedded/mcu8051ide/mcu8051ide-1.3.5.ebuild digest
	5. Modify /etc/make.conf
		...
		PORTDIR_OVERLAY="/usr/local/portage"
		...


Web page:
http://mcu8051ide.sf.net

